node.text: Whoop whoop 🙌 there’s a NEW video and it was loads of fun to make! It’s a vegan budget challenge, and the most ultra-budget meal video we’ve made to-date! Come grocery shopping with us, and then join us over the course of 5 days where we make 5 different delicious meals with those groceries… and each serving comes out to under €1😲😆 video link in profile 📽 #vegan #plantbased

node.text:
Has it felt like a looooong Wednesday for anyone else? Coffee is seriously the life force keeping me going right now 😅

If you enjoy a good ol’ cup of brew but don’t have any coffee apparatus to make it, this cold brew coffee recipe is for you! All you need: coffee beans, a jar, and some cheesecloth (or nut milk bag). 

You can make a big batch of the concentrate, and then you’ve got coffee-on-demand for the next week 🕺🏻 We served it with a homemade vanilla #vegan coffee cream too 🤤 

Full recipe link in profile 🌞 #coffee #humpday #coldbrew #plantbased

node.text: This granola brings together two of my favourite things: granola and chocolate 🍫 I usually top my smoothie bowls and yogurt with crunchy granola, but for a super-fast breakfast, granola with plant-milk or yogurt and some fresh fruit is the way to go 🍓 Meal prep it this weekend to enjoy it all week! Have you made any of our granola recipes yet? Which is your favourite? Recipe link in profile 🌞  #vegan #plantbased #breakfast #mealprep

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sadia Badiei, BSc Dietetics in Pick Up Limes. May be an image of 1 person and sunglasses.

node.text:
We interrupt your regular programming for this appreciation post. Thanks for being here. Thanks for reading this. Thanks for watching our videos and trying our recipes. Thanks to the 1000s of you who’ve left comments and ratings on our recipes. How we got so darn lucky with this PUL family of ours I’ll never know.⁣
⁣
In case you missed it, when we transferred our website from the old one to the new one, we couldn’t transfer over the comments with it. Comments and ratings really help others know which recipes were enjoyed, and so it helps a lot! If it’s not a huge ask, and if you have a moment to spare, could we invite you to share your review on any PUL recipe you’ve tried? It’d be so appreciated💕 I’ll leave our website link in profile 🌱⁣
⁣
Sending our thanks, a virtual hug, and a cupcake if we could 😋 #recipes #vegan #plantbased

node.text:
There's a NEW video on the tube! 🥰⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Moving away from Canada is not something I ever thought I'd do. I moved to the Netherlands for love, but it came with a considerable amount of heartache in missing my family, along with an ongoing nagging feeling that I would need to eventually learn Dutch. I'll say frankly that language learning is not an interest of mine, but in order to be able to continue to stay in the Netherlands, I was required to learn a basic level of Dutch. I was given a generous few years by the government to learn the language, but silly me kept postponing studying. I think in my heart I kept thinking Robin and I would move back to Canada before the deadline approached. But that didn't happen. And the cherry on top: the deadline even got pushed up 5 months, so I had only about 1 week to cram in learning as much Dutch as I possibly could 🇳🇱⁣
⁣
This is that story. Plus the video features the incredible @nathanieldrew_ 🕺🏻 Video link in profile! 🎥 ⁣⁣

node.text: Got some overripe bananas on your counter? This recipe is a delicious way to use them up 🍌🤤! If you couldn't be bothered to make  an entire loaf, or if it's super hot where you are and you'd rather not heat up the house by turning on the oven, then give this speedy, single-serving dessert a try. Recipe link in profile 😊 Happy Friday! #vegan #plantbased

node.text:
Heyooo there’s a NEW videooo💃🏻 whoop whoop!⁣
⁣
We’ve made 3 new meal prep breakfast recipes that are so good, I don’t think I can pick a favourite. There’s a savoury recipe, a cool and refreshing recipe, and a crunchy chocolatey recipe 🤤⁣
⁣
And as if that weren’t enough, we also posted an extra 3 recipes to the website too! A homemade salsa, some baked tortilla chips, aaaand an unbelievably delicious chipotle refried bean recipe 🔥 6 new recipes in one day? Oooh ya 😌⁣
⁣
Check out the video with the link in profile 🙌 #vegan #plantbased #breakfast

node.text:
There’s a NEW video on the tube 😁 3 EPIC salad recipes, with the most easy and delicious 7-ingredient homemade vegan feta you’ll ever try🤤 plus I share my personal formula for making an incredible salad that impresses every time 😉⁣
⁣
We made this video thinking it’d be perfectly in time for the heat of late spring, but it’s been so cold and grey in the Netherlands that I’m still wearing my winter jacket out and about, and I have a blanket on my lap at my desk as I type this 😅. Looking forward to a bit of sun, not gonna lie. How’s the weather been where you’re at? ⁣
⁣
Check out the video with the link in profile 🥒🫐 #vegan #plantbased
